# CSG Design System — SenseCraft AI

You are working in a codebase that follows the **CSG Design System** for SenseCraft AI. The full specification lives in `DESIGN.md` at the project root. Always read it before generating or reviewing UI code.

## Core Rules

### Colors — use CSS custom properties, never hardcode hex
- Primary CTA / active: `var(--primary-500)` (#8FC31F)
- Primary hover: `var(--primary-400)` (#A8E03C)
- Primary pressed: `var(--primary-600)` (#76A219)
- Dark text / teal accent: `var(--secondary-500)` (#003A4A)
- Page / card surface: `var(--white)` (#FFFFFF)
- Recessed chrome (inputs, nav, modal bars): `var(--neutral-50)` (#FAFAFA)
- Default border: `var(--border)` (#E5E5E5)
- Input / modal border: `var(--border-regular)` (#D9D9D9)
- Active / focus border: `var(--border-primary)` (#8FC31F)
- Body text: `var(--neutral-700)` (#404040)
- Heading text: `var(--neutral-900)` (#171717)
- Placeholder / disabled: `var(--neutral-400)` (#A3A3A3)
- Error: `var(--error)` (#DC2626)
- Warning: `var(--warning)` (#FF9500)

### Typography
- EN UI: `'Space Grotesk', ui-sans-serif, system-ui`
- Chinese: `'Noto Sans SC', sans-serif`
- Code / model IDs / metrics / terminal: `'Space Mono', ui-monospace, monospace`
- Negative letter-spacing at heading sizes: -0.01rem at 22px, -0.02rem at 36px, -0.03rem at 48px
- Never reduce CN text size relative to EN — they must match

### Icons — MingCute exclusively
- Import via `@iconify/react` with `mingcute:` prefix
- Always use `*-line` (outline) variants by default
- Only use `*-fill` when semantically required (destructive dialogs, selected states)
- Never use Heroicons, Lucide, Phosphor, or any other icon set

### Border Radius — only these values
- 0 / 4px / 8px / 12px / 16px / 24px / 9999px
- Buttons & inputs: 8px; Cards: 12px; Pills/tags: 9999px

### Elevation
- Cards/panels: borders only (`1px solid #E5E5E5`), no box-shadow
- Shadows only for modals/dropdowns: `0px 10px 24px -6px rgba(0,0,0,0.15)`
- Surface hierarchy via background tone (#FFFFFF vs #FAFAFA), not shadows

### Component Dimensions (from Figma)
- Text button: Small=28px, Default=36px, Large=42px height
- Text input: 42px height, #FAFAFA bg, 8px radius
- Pop-up: 422px wide, 12px radius
- Badge: pill 9999px, 4px 10px padding, 12px font

### Disabled State (all interactive components)
- `opacity: 0.4`
- `cursor: not-allowed`
- No hover/pressed response

### Do NOT
- Hardcode hex values — use CSS custom properties
- Use #8FC31F as a large fill/background — it's an activation signal only
- Use dark teal (#003A4A) as surface background — it's a text/accent color
- Use Space Grotesk for code/model names — use Space Mono
- Mix CN and EN fonts in the same text element
- Add shadows to cards or panels
- Use font-weight 800 for body text — reserve for hero numbers

## Reference
For exact component specs (15 component types with pixel-precise dimensions, states, and variants), see the full `DESIGN.md`.
